reviewText:
Very entertaining and good to unwind from fast paced games! I sincerely hope people pick up a copy of this game, though before you do, I must warn:
-It doesnt have high end graphics;
-The sprint the game is good but how long you can sprint is a bit short;
-The game isnt for ahrdcore shooter fans, its basically a cloak and dagger game all about killing silently or out of sigh;
-It might bget boring if you don't have friends with the game;
However there's a bunch of funs thing, such as the Sims style needs where it makes it interesting how long you can stay hunting and hunted without dying, sleeping or needing to use the bathroom, plus you can also bribe cops to ignore crimes for a small amount of time and also for information, you have an arrawy of weapons and each of them give you a certain amount of cash when you kill with them.

BUT OVER AND ALL, its a good game to play with friends!

